query:
select distinct
                vsp.is_key,
                vsvp.schema_id,
                vsp.v_spec_schema_pattern_id,
                vsp.element_id,
                vsp.attribute_id,
                vsvp.id,
                coalesce(vsp.updated_on, vsp.created_on) as changed_on
            from vehicle_spec_pattern vsp
                join v_spec_schema_pattern vsvp on vsvp.id = vsp.v_spec_schema_pattern_id
            where
                vsp.is_key = '0'
